---
<footer class="bg-[#050505] w-full pt-24 pb-12 border-t border-border/30">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-16 px-6 md:px-12 w-full max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2">
      <a href="/" class="flex flex-col mb-8 group w-fit">
        <span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white uppercase leading-none group-hover:text-primary transition-colors italic">Elite Industrial</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] text-primary uppercase leading-none mt-1">Metalwork</span>
      </a>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-md">
        Εξειδικευμένες μεταλλικές κατασκευές και μηχανολογικές λύσεις υψηλής ακρίβειας. Με πολυετή εμπειρία και σύγχρονο εξοπλισμό, εγγυόμαστε την αντοχή και την ποιότητα σε κάθε έργο.
      </p>
      <div class="flex space-x-6">
        <a class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-primary hover:border-primary transition-all" href="#"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">precision_manufacturing</span></a>
        <a class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-primary hover:border-primary transition-all" href="#"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">settings</span></a>
        <a class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-border flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-primary hover:border-primary transition-all" href="#"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">engineering</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-black text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-8">Πλοήγηση</h4>
      <nav class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" href="/services">Υπηρεσίες</a>
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" href="/projects">Έργα</a>
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" href="/quote">Προσφορά</a>
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-black text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-8">Επικοινωνία</h4>
      <div class="flex flex-col space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">location_on</span>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Βιομηχανική Περιοχή Ασπροπύργου,<br/>Θέση Δύο Πεύκα, 19300</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">call</span>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">+30 210 000 0000</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">mail</span>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">info@elite-industrial.gr</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-border/20 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
    <p class="text-text-muted text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
      © 2025 Elite Industrial Metalwork. All rights reserved.
    </p>
    <div class="flex space-x-8">
      <span class="text-[10px] text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">ISO 9001:2015</span>
      <span class="text-[10px] text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">CE Certified</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
